    <xpath>/Defs/ResearchProjectDef[defName="Research_BasicImmunology"]/description</xpath>
    <value>
      <!-- Original: Study the fundamental principles of the immune system. Develop techniques to culture weakened pathogens and stimulate preventive immune responses. Unlocks flu, plague, and wound infection vaccines. -->
      <description>Study the fundamental principles of the immune system. Develop techniques to culture weakened pathogens and stimulate preventive immune responses. Unlocks wound infection vaccine.</description>
    </value>
  </Operation>
