      <!-- Original: Expand vaccine research to cover parasitic diseases common in tropical and jungle biomes. Develop specialized vaccines against vector-borne parasites and gut parasites. Unlocks malaria, sleeping sickness, gut worms, and lung rot vaccines. -->
      <description>Expand vaccine research to cover malaria, a parasite common in tropical and jungle biomes. Unlocks malaria vaccine.</description>
    </value>
  </Operation>
